version_description:
Hello #fluiger, thank you for using our application! In this new version, we have optimized some features to render fluig even more essential for your business, including in your mobile devices.

Looking for first-hand access to the new features in fluig? Use the automatic application update feature: select “Updates” in “Settings”> “iTunes and App Store”
